      <title>日本民众渴望改变。执政党能实现这一目标吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-09-09/japan-s-ruling-party-the-ldp-must-reinvent-itself-to-stay-relevant</link>
